title: The Tragically Hip - A National Celebration [720p30 H264]
description:
This is a stream dump (not a cam or screen capture) of the entire online broadcast of The Tragically Hip's last performance in Kingston on August 20th 2016 at 20:30 Eastern Time, including CBC's 30-minute post-show. It has not been transcoded at all, but was remuxed in an MKV with chapters added. There are no commercials or interruptions.
 
https://i.sli.mg/7hE9h8.jpg

If you enjoy the broadcast (which should be a given) consider donating to the Gord Downie Fund for Brain Cancer Research at https://donate.sunnybrook.ca/braincancerresearch
